Kadi kabitu anu bipepele to: misangu ya bungi makuta atubu bafuta bua kusumba ndeke wa mushinga mukole atu misangu inayi kupita a ndeke wa bubanji ne misangu 11 kupita a ndeke wa kumpala.
Kabiena ne mushinga bua kulomba difuta dia mushinga mukese mu tshibambalu tshia ndeke tshia mushinga mukole anyi tshia ndeke wa kumpala mu ndeke idi kayiyi ne ndeke bua kumbuka muaba umue kuya muaba mukuabu.
Bua kumanya bimpe ne: bamue bendeshi ba ndeke batu basue kufuta makuta a bungi bua kuenza luendu ne lukasa ne kupeta mashinyi mimpe, bendeshi ba ndeke batu bafuta makuta a mushindu eu.
Tshimenga tshikulu tshia ditunga dia Moldavie ntshia Chişinău, muakulu wabu wa ku dibele ngua tshiena-Roumanie, kadi tshiena-Russie ke tshidi bantu ba bungi bakula.
Mu ditunga dia Moldavie mudi bantu ba bisamba bia bungi badi bapitshile mu bikondo bia bimvundu ne mvita.
Mu 1994, mvita eyi yakapatula ditunga dia Transnistrie ku Est kua ditunga dia Moldavie, divua ne mbulamatadi ne makuta adi kadiyi mamanyike kudi ONU.
Nansha muvua muyuki wa malu a tshididi kawuyi muende bimpe, bakatuadija kupingaja malanda a mpetu pankatshi pa bitupa bibidi bia ditunga dia Moldavie.
Tshitendelelu tshinene tshia mu Moldavie ntshia bena Kristo ba mu Ortodokse.
Izmir ke tshimenga tshisatu tshinene tshia mu ditunga dia Turquie tshidi ne bantu batue ku miliyo 3.
Tshimenga tshia kale tshia Semuna tshidi tshilua tshimenga tshia lelu tshidi ne bubanji bua bungi, tshinyunguluka kudi tshitudilu tshia mazuwa ne mikuna.
Nansha mudi tshimenga etshi tshikale ne njila minene, nzubu ya madidishi ne nzubu ya madidishi ya kale, tshisalu tshia mu lukama lua bidimu lua 18 ne bitanda bia kale, tshidi tshimueneka bu tshimenga tshia ku Mputu wa ku Mediterane pamutu pa kuikala tshia mu Turquie wa kale.
Mu musoko mukese wa Haldarsvík udi pabuipi ne tshidiila tshia Eysturoy, mudi tshitanda tshia dikumi ne muanda mukulu tshia dikema.
Ku mpenga kua tshitanda etshi kudi bimfuanyi bikuabu bia nyunyi bienza ne mabue ne bimane pa mabue.
